{"tid":1563531,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"呢場運動係咪壽終正寢？","createTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-21T04:25:50.000Z","uid":284817,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8b8e81617a9a618d56b4555f7ad84abc3e08d046","tid":1563531,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:17.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">點解冇晒聲氣？</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">今日見到連登啲post好嬲！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">報紙繼續由黨媒買起廣告維穩<br />\n連儂牆俾晒藍屍種族清洗！<br />\n商場畀藍屍放匪旗、唱匪歌！<br />\n狗獲派伸縮狗棍！<br />\n小學教師反被狗家長欺凌！</span><br />\n<br />\n係咪場運動完咗？話我聽！<br />\n<br />\n最起碼嘅和理非文宣去咗邊？<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">國際眾籌登報要繼續！<br />\n連儂牆要繼續！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">戰線唔可以停！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span>"},{"pid":"13265dbc32f829a3632fda9a3ee9afef7f6b4d6f","tid":1563531,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"fa5f805949243c823f898384df6c87e73af33cd5","tid":1563531,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:37.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98ebe731f70b7252655dd796784eddd20416391d","tid":1563531,"uid":284817,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:19:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2f4c244fd10e3e5b4554e8a4a95717eae8ee1b0c","tid":1563531,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T12:20:03.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<